    "created_at": "2014-11-19T07:01:43Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-11-19T07:03:18Z",
    "body": "I personally like my plug-ins telling me what the 'standard' way of formatting is, and then letting me decide _after_ I've become aware of that information whether I'm okay with it or not. I'd rather the technology I use having opinions (esp. 'standard' opinions) that I can take into account than allowing me to blindly charge in.\n",
